ATTRIBUTION

This project is based on homebridge-unifi-occupancy by DouweM:
- Original project: https://github.com/DouweM/homebridge-unifi-occupancy
- Original license: Apache-2.0

Modifications made for homebridge-unifi-occupancy-lite:
- Removed username/password authentication (API tokens only)
- Removed all external dependencies (unifi-events, koa, gravatar, etc.)
- Simplified configuration and removed web server
- Replaced memoization with native lazy properties
- Modernized for Homebridge 2.0+ and Node.js 18+
- Streamlined device detection logic